&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ( bengali : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ; english : hey beautiful bride ) is a 1981 bengali comedy film , directed by salil dutta . it was one of the last films of the iconic bengali actor uttam kumar , who died during production . a lookalike prabir kumar was brought in to stand in for uttam kumar during the final sections of the film , the body double was used in the song " o daddy o mummy " and younger brother &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; kumar 's voice was dubbed in . the music was composed by bappi lahiri . the movie is a bengali reworking of the story of pygmalion , heavily drawing upon the hit british musical my fair lady .